# References — top-level index

Roll-up of every reference doc tracked under `references/`. Topic dirs
each have their own `INDEX.md` with detail. Edit this file when you add
or version-bump a doc.

> **Discipline:** see [CLAUDE.md](../CLAUDE.md#references) "References".
> Don't overwrite — version-bump and update the topic's INDEX. ADRs and
> risks may cite the version current at filing time.

